{"tid":1009463,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【指150個單程證名額安排由來已久　張建宗：家庭團聚是重要】","createTime":"2019-02-05T07:54:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-05T10:36:55.000Z","uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1b95c1f8d8f9fe12efbd3b84950f3e85dfa2765f","tid":1009463,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T07:54:58.000Z","msg":"對於有意見指，每日150個單程證名額，是公立醫院爆煲的其中一個主要原因，政務司司長張建宗表示要實事求事，指每日150個家庭團聚是由來已久的安排。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗稱以人道立場，為香港長遠來說，家庭團聚是重要，又稱這一點大家都了解。他強調完全明白醫護前線人員壓力，所以很感謝他們謹守崗位。人手方面，會盡量吸引已退休醫護人員繼續工作，亦都會吸引外來人才來港，例如是有限度註冊的醫生。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗透露於去年9月，到英國倫敦與部分醫科生及醫生會面時，他指對方都是香港人，其中部分人被打動，考慮回港工作。"},{"pid":"8399c044f4f6cf735e54b9a899bfb3fb2e976aaa","tid":1009463,"uid":39777,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T07:56:36.000Z","msg":"家庭團聚重要，但醫療系統爆煲，你地排唔到公屋就唔重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a07edf53492581ed7d1ffef6838bd55387f358c0","tid":1009463,"uid":36901,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T08:18:48.000Z","msg":"係咁重要就收回審批權<br />\n杜絕賣證假結婚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9b287d6e77d9bc3305a86fc10408f1ac33eb3c9","tid":1009463,"uid":2054,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T08:20:41.000Z","msg":"星架坡收精英<br />\n香港收廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90569abcc761a041c0f29b02caeedc3c09f71def","tid":1009463,"uid":18604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T08:38:00.000Z","msg":"永續團聚"},{"pid":"cc1f7fb9d1f54aa2e1c5522b391b74cf2da65042","tid":1009463,"uid":162490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T08:53:08.000Z","msg":"幾時落去同你d祖先團聚？<br />\n一家團聚最重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce65a7fb04e44523386174207f4b5b99d146c847","tid":1009463,"uid":118127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T10:16:26.000Z","msg":"揾人打柒佢啦屌"},{"pid":"a274c4b8b463079df7daaad9c7faa1741489f80b","tid":1009463,"uid":101945,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T10:20:36.000Z","msg":"中國強大 發展機遇多<br />\n圑聚請到中國"},{"pid":"8529ce433f3aece97fc58162e78e01914672415a","tid":1009463,"uid":52651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T10:22:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YTtfQah.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYTtfQah.jpg&h=943df88d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n認撚住呢班仆街!"},{"pid":"598d8da7bb2e0ac4516d325224c2446e9933ea15","tid":1009463,"uid":192052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T10:32:24.000Z","msg":"垃圾 專材"},{"pid":"c7e09b26eeb81f082599719aa82001513cefd80c","tid":1009463,"uid":63154,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T10:36:55.000Z","msg":"家庭團聚唔會停架咩？咁多年乜家人都落晒黎啦，請政府解釋吓好喎"}]}